Program: Free Thinking
Title: Matthew Barzun, Speed-the-Plow Review
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04jjnm1
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 2 Oct 2014
At a time when the special relationship between the UK and the US is under particular scrutiny, Anne McElvoy talks to the American Ambassador to Britain, Matthew Barzun, about the politics of power and takes a look at sexual politics in Hollywood in the new Anglo-American production of David Mamet's Speed-the-Plow, starring Lindsay Lohan and Richard Schiff. Producer: Harry Parker Photo Credit: Simon Annand. Show less